sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant Gateway as vLLM Orchestrator Gateway<br/>8090/TCP HTTP
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails Orchestrator<br/>8085/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Detectors as Content Detectors
    participant vLLM as vLLM Model Server

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 1: Non-Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token<br/>Content-Type: application/json
    Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector specifications<br/>into request payload
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>Authorization: forwarded<br/>x-forwarded-*: forwarded<br/>Optional mTLS client cert
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: Forward to LLM
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: Model response
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run output detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: JSON response<br/>(with detection metadata)
    Note over Gateway: Check for detections<br/>If detected + fallback configured:<br/>replace content with fallback msg
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON response<br/>(original or fallback)

    Note over Client,vLLM: Flow 2: Streaming Chat Completion with Content Detection (SSE)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /{route}/v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true<br/>Authorization: Bearer Token
    Note over Gateway: Load route config<br/>Inject detector specifications
    Gateway->>Orchestrator: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>stream: true<br/>Optional mTLS
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Run input detectors
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results

    loop Each SSE chunk
        Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: {chunk JSON}
        Note over Gateway: Parse chunk<br/>Check for detections<br/>Apply fallback per-chunk if needed
        Gateway-->>Client: data: {chunk JSON}<br/>(original or fallback)
    end

    Orchestrator-->>Gateway: data: [DONE]
    Gateway-->>Client: data: [DONE]
